headline.print_headline: Dodgers RHP Josh Beckett Won't Return This Season
headline.main: Dodgers RHP Josh Beckett Won't Return This Season

lead_paragraph: Josh Beckett won't return to the mound for the Los Angeles Dodgers this season, and the injured pitcher is mulling retirement.
